item.title: CVE-2021-31339|2024-08-03T22:55:53.551Z -- siemens -- mendix%20excel%20importer%20module
item.description: A vulnerability has been identified in Mendix Excel Importer Module (All versions < V9.0.3). Uploading a manipulated XML File results in an exception that could expose information about the Application-Server and the used XML-Framework.
